title: RHONY: Go to Cancun, Not to Can'tcun
description:
This episode also avail as video on Crappens On Demand http://bit.ly/crappensvideo
Ramona is mad on The Real Housewives of New York, and she takes it out on a poor ceviche guy. Will Leah put her in her place or will their trip go from Cancun go to a trip of Can'tcun? For this week's premium bonus about Netflix' new show Indian Matchmaking, become a member over at Patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens.
